      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    },
    {
      "name": "sesame oil",
      "amount": "2 tablespoons"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the lardons and cook until crispy, then set aside.",
    "Add the pork slices and cook until browned, then set aside with the lardons.",
    "Add the harissa spice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken broth, soy sauce, and ramen noodles, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked pork and lardons back into the pot and stir to combine.",
    "Serve the ramen in a Korean brass bowl and garnish with green onions."
